Germany’s Roesler Opposes Raising Taxes for Alternative Energy

-- B y   A l l i s o n   C o n n o l l y
-- 
2011-04-16T14:28:26Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-16/germany-s-roesler-opposes-raising-taxes-for-alternative-energy.html
German Health Minister Philipp Roesler, who’s running to become leader of the Free Democratic
Party, said his party opposes raising taxes to pay for
alternative energy to replace nuclear power, the  Passauer Neuen
Press e quoted him as saying.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Allison Connolly in  Frankfurt  at 
 aconnolly4@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Phil Serafino at   pserafino@bloomberg.net . 